source_repo: https://github.com/tyroneross/Omniparse
source_path: packages/sdk
upstream_commit: 392acf8eeb5df898309d16051a8e06ae80bbe86d
upstream_version: 1.0.0
upstream_license: FSL-1.1-MIT
vendored_on: 2026-04-18
build_notes: |
  Rebuilt locally with tsup.config.ts modified to inline all dependencies
  (xlsx, sax, p-limit) via `noExternal: [/.*/]`. Original tsup.config in
  upstream declares `external: ['xlsx', 'sax']`, which would produce a
  dist that requires node_modules at runtime. The inlined build produces
  a single self-contained dist/bin/omniparse.js with zero external
  `require()` calls for runtime deps.
  Verification: `grep -E "require\(\"(xlsx|sax|p-limit)\"\)" dist/bin/omniparse.js` → 0 matches.
